item.title: Hidden San Diego
item.description: Much in the vein of the fantastic Atlas Obscura but specific to the San Diego area. I’ve lived here my whole life and honestly boo a little when another favorite place gets posted. That is to say they are pretty good at surfacing some rad stuff, and indeed the commons can become tragic.
